Nicki Minaj’s father, Robert Maraj, is dead. TMX reports that he died after a hit-and-run accident. Nassau County Police in New York said Robert was walking between Roslyn Road and Raff Avenue Friday evening around 6 PM ET. A vehicle heading northbound hit him and the driver fled the scene. Robert was rushed to a hospital where he passed on at the weekend. The Homicide Squad is investigating the case, although there is no adequate description of the suspect’s vehicle yet.